<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Page non configurée</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
    }
    .icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    p {
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="icon">⚙️</div>
    <h1>Page en cours de configuration</h1>
    <p>Cette landing page n'a pas encore de fichier HTML principal défini. L'administrateur doit configurer la page pour la rendre accessible.</p>
    <span class="badge">Bientôt disponible</span>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
